---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
const today = "10 December 2025";
---

<Layout>
    <div class="page-container">
        <h1>Cancellation & Refund Policy</h1>
        <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> {today}</p>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>1. Subscription Cancellation</h2>
            <p>
                Users may cancel their subscription at any time. Cancellation
                prevents future billing but does not refund previous payments.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>2. Refund Eligibility</h2>
            <p>
                MiSkills provides instant access to digital learning content,
                therefore subscription payments are generally non-refundable.
            </p>
            <p>
                Refunds may be issued only in special cases such as duplicate
                payments or failed transactions.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>3. Refund Processing</h2>
            <p>
                Approved refunds will be processed to the original payment
                method within 5–7 business days as per Razorpay’s settlement
                timelines.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>

<style>
    .page-container {
        max-width: 750px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
        font-family: Inter, system-ui, sans-serif;
        color: #111;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    h2 {
        font-size: 1.4rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-top: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    p,
    li {
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        line-height: 1.75rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: #444;
    }

    ul {
        padding-left: 1.25rem;
    }

    strong {
        color: #000;
    }

    .section {
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    }
</style>
